  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle your way through the horde of evil undead. Upgrade weapons, place traps, throw axes, and take advantage of various perks to fit your badass zombie-slaying style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1667590/extras/42fe41f7e90c812405631c2fa7e48e72.avif?t=1764012815\" width=800 height=538 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Each Wave Brings New Terror</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive wave after wave as enemies grow in power and number. Use scrap collected from lootables and enemies to upgrade your arsenal.  Duke it out with the undead and survive as long as you can!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle your way through the horde of evil undead. Upgrade weapons, place traps, throw axes, and take advantage of various perks to fit your badass zombie-slaying style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1667590/extras/42fe41f7e90c812405631c2fa7e48e72.avif?t=1764012815\" width=800 height=538 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Each Wave Brings New Terror</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive wave after wave as enemies grow in power and number. Use scrap collected from lootables and enemies to upgrade your arsenal.  Duke it out with the undead and survive as long as you can!</p>",
